  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nAccording to the [Validator Client API documentation](https://lighthouse-book.sigmaprime.io/api-vc-endpoints.html#post-lighthousevalidators), all requests (GET, POST, PATCH) must contain Authorization header with the token.\r\n\r\nThe current implementation only requires the API token in GET requests only, POST/PATCH requests will be processed even if they don't contain the Authorization header.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/blob/stable/validator_client/src/http_api/mod.rs#L480\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6521369/129372547-baf6cee8-fbc5-4524-a88c-c02ab1fbbcbd.png)\r\n\r\n\r\ncc: @Nocasis",
