    "body": "Hey @paulhauner.\r\n\r\n```\r\ncurl -X PATCH localhost:5062/lighthouse/validators\r\n{\"code\":400,\"message\":\"BAD_REQUEST: missing Authorization header\",\"stacktraces\":[]}\r\n```\r\nYour example is incorrect. There is no such endpoint in the API.\r\n\r\nI attached two requests illustrating that PATCH requests don't require tokens.\r\nPlease fix.\r\n\r\n![photo_2021-08-18_10-06-52](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6521369/129830640-d2ddba58-e229-4cc8-aa6c-33f5d4f3c408.jpg)\r\n\r\n![photo_2021-08-18_10-20-54](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6521369/129831755-c5685415-e0a1-4d0a-8472-6a5789d763e0.jpg)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
